overview.en: As a native token issued by Truedeal platform, TDT is a kind of digital voucher of rights and interests that can be used to trade second-hand idle products in Truedeal ecosystem, including purchase and sale, traceability, arbitration, and maintenance of the products.
overview.zh: TDT是Truedeal平臺發行的原生代幣，是一種數字權益憑證，可以在Truedeal生態圈內進行全球範圍的二手閒置品交易，包括貨品的買賣、溯源、仲裁、維護等。
